{"tid":1680320,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"另一半有抑鬱真係好辛苦","createTime":"2019-10-28T17:41:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T08:31:45.000Z","uid":301809,"like":71,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"489dc96fe2ba62becb4cc14f0440fac370305987","tid":1680320,"uid":301809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T17:41:12.000Z","msg":"每日就係不停咁去聽佢放負，望住佢日日都好唔開心嘅樣，每日又要諗唔同嘅說話去氹翻佢，但去到夜晚佢又會whatsapp打一段野畀我，再delete翻以為我瞓咗睇唔到。其實久而久之自己都好大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇人明白"},{"pid":"29273b26e2ab5e384a8a18c8970c8011e3cdd9d5","tid":1680320,"uid":141237,"like":29,"dislike":2,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T17:46:38.000Z","msg":"好彩之前無簡依type女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實香港有好多人都有中度抑鬱"},{"pid":"79caa5e76499f74b8032e1d21786d4164448c27e","tid":1680320,"uid":45353,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T18:01:49.000Z","msg":"咁你自己抑鬱化<br />\n<br />\n咪可以平等互助互愛"},{"pid":"a041deaaba5cf4410cc3811f672d5193fccd1682","tid":1680320,"uid":195252,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T19:06:14.000Z","msg":"睇醫生係好重要，病向淺中醫"},{"pid":"f5e85f04d37c33d90d5813ba3a75d394a8c07220","tid":1680320,"uid":300642,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T19:08:53.000Z","msg":"有套日本電影叫我老公有抑鬱症，堺雅人同宮崎葵主演，幾催淚，睇完可能你會重新搵返動力"},{"pid":"f419ba3c9271b7c4640be197ec11a2ee9e537ed1","tid":1680320,"uid":313630,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T19:51:42.000Z","msg":"所以咪冇心機拍拖住<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等健康啲先"},{"pid":"eec570fce3a7ca6e6ab7458228335922bb004a33","tid":1680320,"uid":319969,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T20:36:02.000Z","msg":"我男朋友都有抑鬱呀<br />\n但係佢依家好少同我呻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢話日日都係咁都無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明我聽完佢呻個人都唔會有壓力<br />\n我淨係擔心佢翻工翻學唔開心<br />\n<br />\n但我好鍾意陪住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c00404503aa7e72c59bd95d23f900e83ba7f3a3","tid":1680320,"uid":319969,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a041deaaba5cf4410cc3811f672d5193fccd1682","tid":1680320,"uid":195252,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T19:06:14.000Z","msg":"睇醫生係好重要，病向淺中醫"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T20:39:54.000Z","msg":"睇醫生唔係咁容易架<br />\n首先你要揾個信得過既醫生<br />\n廢事俾佢篤灰<br />\n然後佢又可能會擔心人地對佢有異見<br />\n又怕影響到工作啊嗰啲<br />\n怕俾人知道佢有病<br />\n唔係你諗一有情緒問題就去睇咁輕鬆架<br />\n<br />\n我都好辛苦地揾到個信得過既醫生<br />\n但男朋友唔想睇<br />\n我都唔逼佢了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a26a6ccb09df2f79e699b8ef0cbe9ea3f48e5939","tid":1680320,"uid":71671,"like":9,"dislike":10,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"489dc96fe2ba62becb4cc14f0440fac370305987","tid":1680320,"uid":301809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T17:41:12.000Z","msg":"每日就係不停咁去聽佢放負，望住佢日日都好唔開心嘅樣，每日又要諗唔同嘅說話去氹翻佢，但去到夜晚佢又會whatsapp打一段野畀我，再delete翻以為我瞓咗睇唔到。其實久而久之自己都好大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇人明白"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T23:46:16.000Z","msg":"放手吧⋯⋯你根本唔夠鍾意佢。<br />\n好多人覺得拍拖都係想開心，但果種開心其實係邊個俾你都得。<br />\n搵個玩得嘅拍下散拖算啦！"},{"pid":"e0c63864e283efb2fd6089a3176469ca27a57b17","tid":1680320,"uid":265153,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T03:58:17.000Z","msg":"好難捱架 我覺得唔可以話有病就大哂 大家一定要傾下都搵到個平衡，如果唔係你一係死頂 一係去到最後頂唔順分手.拍拖最重要都係溝通 如果大家收收埋埋咩都唔講就話為對方好既 咁仲叫唔叫拍拖呢？加油啊樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申A0毒撚 不起勿插<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6af6c0d9b752934b251c47d3261bc6fd9392e42","tid":1680320,"uid":230197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T04:35:01.000Z","msg":"飛"},{"pid":"9f89cc451fe5c2c855304f5c45186e21d5b610d1","tid":1680320,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"